      "id": "cmrc58hmezub0",
      "column": "done",
      "title": "Add Automation TCs on Bench-Status board",
      "desc": "Playwright + TypeScript E2E test suite for the board (26 tests):\n\nview-board-overview.spec.ts (2)\n- Board renders all 4 columns with their cards\n- Summary chips reflect card counts\n\ntoggle-theme.spec.ts (1)\n- Theme toggle switches and persists across reload\n\nview-board-as-guest.spec.ts (2)\n- No editing controls rendered without a GitHub token\n- Avatar is not editable without a token\n\nmanage-cards-as-owner.spec.ts (6)\n- \"+\" button only appears in the To Do column\n- Adding a card places it in the chosen column, updates counter\n- Editing a card updates its title\n- Deleting a card removes it, decrements counter\n- A card with no title cannot be saved\n- Adding a custom tag persists it on the card\n\nview-card-details.spec.ts (5)\n- Shows description, dates and tags for the selected card\n- Shows a link to the certificate when the card has one\n- Guest cannot edit from the detail view\n- Owner can jump from detail view straight into editing\n- Escape closes the detail view\n\nconnect-github-token.spec.ts (2)\n- Connecting a token unlocks the owner UI\n- Removing the token locks the UI again\n\nsave-board-to-github.spec.ts (3, mocked GitHub API)\n- Save commits the board and shows a success message\n- First-time publish omits sha when no file exists yet\n- A failed save shows an error, leaves the change unsaved\n\ndrag-card-between-columns.spec.ts (1)\n- Dragging a card moves it, updates both counters\n\nupload-avatar.spec.ts (1)\n- Uploading an image replaces the monogram with the photo\n\ncollapse-columns-on-mobile.spec.ts (3)\n- Done column starts collapsed, others expanded\n- Tapping a header toggles collapsed/expanded\n- Tapping the Done header expands it",
